  "year": "2026",
  "abstract": "A multicentric European study investigated the seroprevalence of influenza D virus (IDV) in domestic cats and dogs. Serum samples from Italy, France and Ukraine (2015-2018, 2020, 2023-2024) showed no IDV positivity in Italy or in France. In Ukraine, 2.46% of dogs and 0.85% of cats tested positive in 2024.",
